data.text: I stayed twice at Five Palm and gotta say it is a fun place. Great view to the ocean and to the city of Dubai/JBR. But you need to be into parties and louder music also in daytime. It is worth staying there if you are into partying.
data.title: Great entertainment and beautiful view

data.title: Nice place in dubai
